                </div>
                <p>At the core of the KTM 390 Adventure R lies the latest generation of KTM's venerable single-cylinder engine, now enlarged and thoroughly refined.</p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">A New Era of Power: The 399cc LC4c Engine</span></p>
                <p><span class="font-weight-700">The 2025 390 Adventure R </span>is expected to be powered by the all-new<span class="font-weight-700"> 398.7 cc LC4c, liquid-cooled, single-cylinder engine</span>. This engine is a significant evolution from the previous 373 cc unit, focusing on delivering a smoother, more accessible power delivery while still maintaining KTM's signature punch.</p>
